The 14th edition of the prestigious Headies award held on Sunday. The event, which was virtual due to COVID-19 pandemic, was hosted by funnyman Bovi and Nancy Isime. Fast-rising singers like Fireboy DML, Bad Boy Timz and Omah Lay received their first plaques. Fireboy was the biggest winner at the 14th Headies on Sunday night snagging four awards — including the ‘Best R&B Single’, ‘Best R&B Album’, ‘Headies revelation’, and ‘Best Pop Album’ categories.